    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚大学校长沙菲克在数月校园骚乱后辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/columbia-president-shafik-resigns-citing-turmoil-and-divisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚大学校长米努什·沙菲克在加沙战争抗议活动引发的动荡时期后辞职，成为常春藤盟校中第三位因与冲突和校园反犹太主义指控相关的动荡而离职的校长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/columbia-president-shafik-resigns-citing-turmoil-and-divisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 00:15:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国政局动荡表明保皇派仍在掌权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-political-upheaval-shows-royalists-still-firmly-in-charge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国领导人上任不到一年就被赶下台，这清楚地表明了一件事：过去二十年来，在军方支持下长期实行统治的保皇派政权仍然掌握着全部权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/thai-political-upheaval-shows-royalists-still-firmly-in-charge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
